OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSchool holidays: Could     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWales' summer break be cut 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fto four weeks?             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, School summer holidays in Wales could  
OL,6, be cut to as little as four weeks as   
OL,7, part of a shake-up of term times.      
OL,9,FWelsh government education minister    
OL,10,FJeremy Miles has ruled out cutting the 
OL,11,Fbreak to two or three weeks or having  
OL,12,Ffewer holidays.                        
OL,14,FOne union said there were "many more   
OL,15,Fpressing issues that need attention".  
OL,17,FMr Miles said public research showed   
OL,18,Fwhile there was "reasonable            
OL,19,Fcontentment" with the timetable there, 
OL,20,Fwas "openness" to change.              
